haunted me these last few weeks?

281
00:14:24,765 --> 00:14:26,355
A tiny bit, yeah.

282
00:14:27,738 --> 00:14:29,506
And now, clearly, Betty and Jughead,

283
00:14:29,509 --> 00:14:31,431
you guys are caught up in the aftermath.

284
00:14:31,434 --> 00:14:34,605
So to clear the air amongst us,

285
00:14:34,608 --> 00:14:36,770
Jughead and I

286
