289
00:14:43,450 --> 00:14:45,316
Well, wait a minute, I don't know.

290
00:14:45,318 --> 00:14:46,383
Hold on.

291
00:14:47,386 --> 00:14:50,621
Veronica and I kissing
might help to, uh...

292
