00:22:19,208 --> 00:22:22,072
Unless that was some seriously
aggressive hand-holding

427
00:22:22,075 --> 00:22:23,546
I heard through the wall last night...

428
00:22:24,636 --> 00:22:26,150
When did that start?

429
00:22:27,606 --> 00:22:30,206
The night of your confirmation.

430
00:22:30,209 --> 00:22:32,075
- Really?
- Mmm-hmm.

431
00:22:32,077 --> 00:22:33,877
Well,

