Yes.

464
00:23:58,830 --> 00:24:01,865
But you can make it up to
me by remembering one thing.

465
00:24:01,867 --> 00:24:05,004
And it's simple and non-negotiable.

466
00:24:05,007 --> 00:24:08,121
From now on, it's me and you,

467
00:24:08,124 --> 00:24:10,658
not you and my dad, okay?

468
