489
00:25:15,457 --> 00:25:18,079
Mr. Lodge is the one evicting
people from the trailer park?

490
00:25:18,082 --> 00:25:20,209
No, technically, he
cleared us of our debts

491
00:25:20,211 --> 00:25:21,577
and revoked the evictions.

492
00:25:21,579 --> 00:25:23,446
